  openingDialogue:
  - speaker: Country Mouse
    content: 'Are these all edible? '
  - speaker: CIty Mouse
    content: "Of course. You can eat as much as you want, as long as you don\u2019t
      get caught. "
  - speaker: Country Mouse
    content: "(eating) So delicious\u2026 I\u2019ve never had food like this before. "
  - speaker: City Mouse
    content: "That\u2019s why I said, your life back there is way too boring. "
  - speaker: Country Mouse
    content: "(shifting) Maybe\u2026 a little. "
  - speaker: City Mouse
    content: "No more talking\u2014let\u2019s just enjoy it together first. "
